jobInfo.postDescription:
Your work will focus on these responsibilities:
•	Together with line manager to identify and prioritize the operational improvement needs in the company through both direct observations and analytics. Consider the whole value chain when prioritizing improvement needs.
•	Develop applications that effectively accomplish user objectives and needs
•	Design and write code for applications
•	Analyse and edit existing computer applications to improve functionality
•	Remodel and adapt applications as needed to optimize performance
•	Install applications and confirm proper communication between equipment and systems
•	Identify specific customer and client needs and preferences related to application
•	Test applications extensively to ensure they are error and bug free
•	Act as a technical advisor to all departments
•	Maintain computer applications databases
•	Act as resident technological expert advisor for our products
•	Customize specialized applications according to user needs
•	Create and present application prototypes
•	Collaborate with Wartsila global innovation departments (Mechatronics Analytics & Sys.integration) to develop digital tools for Suzhou plant.
.
To be successful in this role, we expect you to have:
•	Well master of Java, familiar with open source framework like Spring/Spring boot/Spring Security/JPA or My batis
•	Experienced in MYSQL, familiar with SQL optimization.
•	Basic skill of using Azure cloud service or Ali cloud server(Linux OS).
•	Can use Angular or VUEor React front-end framework.
•	Can develop mobile application (internal use).
•	Can use GIT and have good coding habits.
•	Good skill of using Microsoft ( Excel, Word, Power Point). Power BI knowledge is preferred.
•	Good English, both written and oral.
jobInfo.address: 苏州虎丘区瓦锡兰船用设备(苏州)有限公司鸿禧路77号

brandComInfo.introduce:
瓦锡兰集团（Wartsila）是全球领先的船舶动力供应商和陆用电站及支持性服务方案的主要提供者，是船厂、船东、船运企业和近海海洋工程项目值得信赖的动力供应商，目前在全球70多个国家拥有140家分支机构和18000多名员工。瓦锡兰中国（Wartsila in China）总部位于上海浦东，并在香港、北京、广州、大连、青岛和江苏、浙江等地设有办事处、独资或合资工厂,员工人数超过2000人。
苏州新区的瓦锡兰船用设备（苏州）有限公司是瓦锡兰集团的全资子公司，成立于1998年。主要生产全系列的船用污水处理设备、惰性气体生产装置及船用真空盥洗系列产品，95%的产品用于出口。

近年来，集团内部的其它产品仍在有计划地陆续向苏州工厂转移。公司在成立以来的十年中，成功地积累了其产品及市场的经验，发展迅速。年销售额近2亿元人民币。
随着公司业务的快速发展，现诚邀您的加入，携手共创美好未来
